description:
GM Rally : 

Game Release Date
23 January 2009 Worldwide
game mode single player
System requirements Core 2 Duo 2.13 GHz, 1 GB RAM, graphic card 256 MB (GeForce 7900 or better), 1.5 GB HDD, Windows XP
GM Rally is a virtual trial for real cars!
One of the leading car manufacturers in the world introduces a huge variety of different vehicles - from small city cars to powerful off-road monsters. Find one to your liking!
Choose a car, tune and upgrade it, beat your opponents on the track. Prove your skills and tame the wild horses hidden under the hood! Start your engines, the circuit awaits!
Key Features:
Opel, Chevrolet and Saab cars, each one with multiply racing parameters.
25 original tracks on the Mediterranean coast, including France and Spain.
Plenty options to tune your car.
Realistic damage models and authentic car behavior on the track.
source: http://www.1cpublishing.eu/game/gm-rally/overview
